3**************************
Scenario-Based Examples:


| Scenario                                                                 | Expected Behavior                                                                                          |
| ------------------------------------------------------------------------ | ---------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------- |
| **Job takes 90s, initial timeout is 30s**                             | Visibility is extended every 10s ‚Üí message never becomes visible prematurely.                              |
| **Pod crashes at 20s with 30s timeout**                               | Message reappears after \~30s for retry ‚Üí fast recovery. No manual retry logic needed.                     |
| **Job takes between 10s‚Äì120s depending on payload**                   | Short timeout + dynamic extension = fast retry on crash and no over-blocking on short messages.            |
| **Static timeout of 600s for all jobs, even if many complete in 20s** | Wastes queue time ‚Üí dynamic extension reduces queue wait time, making fast jobs reattemptable sooner.      |
| **SIGTERM received during processing at 45s of a 60s task**            | `shutdown` flag avoids deleting the message ‚Üí it becomes visible again safely after last extended timeout. |
| **Downstream system is slow (e.g., payment API delay)**                | Visibility extension keeps message invisible for longer ‚Üí avoids early retry and duplicate API calls.      |

